as/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.poster.avif?t=1754042908\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.webm?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142330/extras/09232d1c6cd7393096f61ffdfb700c4e.mp4?t=1754042908\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
